== PeepCode Thinking Sphinx Address Book Project

This is a project to accompany the PeepCode book on Thinking Sphinx by Pat Allan, available at http://peepcode.com for only US$9.

  http://peepcode.com/products/thinking-sphinx-pdf

This code is provided for educational purposes only. Follow along with the PDF to learn how to install and use Thinking Sphinx.

== Branches

We've made a branch for each subsection in the book. Use the "all branches" menu or clone the entire repository and checkout each branch.

  git branch --track simple_index origin/simple_index
